                "comment": "Professor Ramirez is very responsive, understanding, and interested in her work. There is a lot of reading and lectures are sometimes slow but this course is still very engaging and informative. The interview assignment was very fun but the bulk of your grade depends on a group project so chose groups wisely. ",
                "difficulty_rating": 2,
                "quality_rating": 5
            },
            {
                "comment": "Professor Ramirez is one of the kindest professors on campus. She truly cares about her students and is highly respected. She radiates a high level of knowledge on the topics she teaches and she is always willing to meet with students outside of class, even beyond office hours. Professor Ramirez wants to help her students grow.",
                "difficulty_rating": 3,
                "quality_rating": 5
